  "content": "Great Job Alex!\n\nOne thing though -- I didn't see a way to connect via a browser extension (NIP-07).  \n\nI am actually thinking of building an NIP-46 Continuum Bunker extension so I can  login to NostrHub.io without sharing my nsec\n\nmy Continuum Signer is open sourced by the way:\n\nthe signer specifically -- \n\n(this can be adapted for any application running locally that exposes the sign and public key urls)\n\nhttps://github.com/andrewgstanton/continuum/blob/main/browser_extensions/README_CONTINUUM_SIGNER.md\n\nhttps://github.com/andrewgstanton/continuum",
